channel.title: Does anyone here ACTUALLY know Java?
channel.description:
I'm surprised... I've been a member of these forums for several years now, never really got into the community though. I come back today out of boredom, read a few threads, and the majority of them scare me.
What I'm wondering is: does anyone here actually know how to code java? Like actually know?
I got in an msn conversation with a guy today, this is how it went:
him: I'm probably the best java coder here! me: doubt it. him: I code "3D HD content 508" me: and that proves what exactly? me: here, lets do a test, shall we? me: what's a hashmap? him: no clue lol
Is everyone here like this, or are there actually a few good coders that everyone else is feeding off of?
